<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="away-adv">away <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'weɪ/    美 /ə'weɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>离；离开；间隔：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Go / Run away!
走/跑开！</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His speech is <strong>away from</strong> the subject.
他的讲话离题了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sea is only two miles <strong>away from</strong> here.
大海离这儿只有两英里。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The sports meet is two weeks away.
离运动会还有两个星期。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>朝另一个方向：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t look away while driving.
开车时不要四处张望。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>在别处；在适当的地方：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He put his tools away.
他把工具收起来了。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>不在；外出：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is away in town.
他去城里了。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.<strong>[多与动词连用] ...去；...掉：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>wash away
冲走；冲掉</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The snow melted away. 
雪融化了。</p></div></div>